Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.52,0:00:01.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an5}CONFESSION
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.73,0:00:02.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,CONFESSION
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.73,0:00:05.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}You fall in love with someone...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.40,0:00:08.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}P-Please be my girlfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.27,0:00:09.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}confess that love...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.65,0:00:14.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}and become a couple.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.03,0:00:19.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everyone would say that's a wonderful thing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.62,0:00:23.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}But they're wrong!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.04,0:00:26.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even among sweethearts,\Nthere exists a distinct power relationship!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.96,0:00:29.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}A side that exploits\Nand a side that's exploited,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.42,0:00:31.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}a side that's devoted,\Na side receiving devotion,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.59,0:00:33.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}a winner and a loser!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.01,0:00:41.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you're trying to live a noble life,\Nthen you mustn't become a loser!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.52,0:00:43.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Love is war!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.73,0:00:46.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an5}CONFESSION
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.98,0:00:47.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an5}CONFESSION
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.86,0:00:52.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}The person who falls in love loses!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.52,0:00:55.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}KAGUYA-SAMA: LOVE IS WAR
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.58,0:02:29.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shuchiin Academy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.67,0:02:33.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's a prestigious school\Nwith an ancient and honorable origin,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.38,0:02:35.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}founded as a facility\Nto educate upper-crust children.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.26,0:02:38.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}The focus on the nobility is gone,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.55,0:02:41.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}but many talented students\Nborn into wealthy, distinguished families,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.93,0:02:44.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}and shouldering the future\Nattend the school.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.01,0:02:47.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And now a message\Nfrom the student council.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.43,0:02:50.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The student council members.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.02,0:02:54.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naturally ordinary people wouldn't be permitted\Nto lead and bring these students together!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.48,0:02:59.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kaguya Shinomiya, the vice-president\Nof the student council at Shuchiin Academy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.49,0:03:01.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Total assets: 200 trillion yen.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.16,0:03:04.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her family owns the Shinomiya Group,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.70,0:03:09.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}one of the top four financial conglomerates\Nin Japan, with over 1,000 subsidiaries.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.41,0:03:08.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}SHINOMIYA BANK
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.00,0:03:12.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Befitting her superior lineage,\Nshe's a talented young woman{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.54,0:03:15.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}who has attained\Nsplendid achievements in various fields,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.00,0:03:17.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}such as traditional performing arts,\Nmusic and martial arts.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.71,0:03:20.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}That is Kaguya Shinomiya.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.51,0:03:23.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}And the young man Shinomiya supports is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.85,0:03:28.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Miyuki Shirogane, the president\Nof the student council at Shuchiin Academy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.97,0:03:31.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's wise and intelligent,\Nstrong and silent.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.02,0:03:32.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}He scores first place\Nin the practice exams!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.98,0:03:35.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}In contrast to talented Kaguya,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.11,0:03:37.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}his devotion to studying\Ncommands awe and fear,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.61,0:03:39.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}and because of that exemplary behavior,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.61,0:03:44.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}PRESIDENT OF STUDENT COUNCIL
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.94,0:03:42.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}he was selected to be\Nthe student council president,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.11,0:03:43.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}despite being relatively new to the school.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.62,0:03:47.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}The weight of a solid gold braided cord\Nhas been passed down{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.70,0:03:50.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}from president to president\Nat Shuchiin Academy for 200 years!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.50,0:03:52.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's all!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.55,0:04:01.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,They always look so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.30,0:04:05.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes, when they're together,\Nthey seem even more noble and elegant!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.64,0:04:07.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I still wonder if they're dating.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.97,0:04:11.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What? I'd be shocked if they were!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.31,0:04:16.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I always wonder what they talk about\Nin the student council room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.77,0:04:19.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}STUDENT COUNCIL ROOM
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.78,0:04:21.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,P-President!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.53,0:04:23.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}WHAT WOULD YOU DO?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.78,0:04:24.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You finally bought a smartphone?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.61,0:04:29.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,KAGUYA WANTS TO TRADE
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.03,0:04:31.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}GLITTER
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.82,0:04:27.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}It's got Line, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.08,0:04:29.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Then let's exchange ID's!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.24,0:04:31.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's the age of I.T.!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.79,0:04:34.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Cheap cell phone! It's got a cheap SIM card!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.20,0:04:34.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even Shirogane, a stubborn cheapskate{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.12,0:04:36.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}who's long insisted\Nthat smartphones are unnecessary,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.79,0:04:36.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}- Trendy! Trendy!\N- I'll send it over to you by Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.04,0:04:38.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}has finally given in and gotten one.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.54,0:04:38.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}GLITTER
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.46,0:04:43.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}It doesn't even need to be said how important\Nsmartphones are for high school life.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.84,0:04:40.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Very nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.92,0:04:43.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}I love how you can do so many things with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.84,0:04:46.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}You can use them for social plans\Nor just idly chatting,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.39,0:04:49.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}but sometimes you may not get a reply,\Nso joy can swing to sorrow.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.22,0:04:52.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's possible to confess love to someone\Nusing the Line social app.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.06,0:04:56.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes! This past half-year was wasted,\Nbecause he wasn't using Line!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.98,0:05:00.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}All right, ask me for my ID\Nanytime, Shinomiya!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.69,0:05:04.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yay! I got your ID!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.61,0:05:08.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Why hasn't she asked me?\NIt's my personal information!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.70,0:05:12.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Never mind. Should I just ask her?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.33,0:05:13.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.50,0:05:16.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Asking for contact information,\Nbetween the lines,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.12,0:05:18.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}that indicates a degree of desperation\Nand ulterior motive,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.71,0:05:20.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}which then beget a special meaning...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.59,0:05:24.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}That meaning is, in fact, love!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.51,0:05:28.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}In a romantic relationship, "the person\Nwho falls in love loses" is an absolute rule!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.76,0:05:31.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Confirming your love for someone\Nequals defeat!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.35,0:05:35.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Asking the opposite sex for their contact\Ninformation is as good as a confession of love!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.68,0:05:38.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Apparently, the president\Nis in love with the vice-president!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.60,0:05:40.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Seriously? I have to share that!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.61,0:05:44.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}For a boy going through puberty,\Nthat means death!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.82,0:05:46.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Forget it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.45,0:05:48.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no way I can ask her!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.24,0:05:50.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Shinomiya, you ask me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.87,0:05:56.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}I'm sure the president is waiting for me\Nto ask him, but he'd better not hold his breath.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.29,0:06:02.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}It would mean something if he came to me\Nand asked, even though he was embarrassed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.42,0:06:04.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Conflict! It's an inevitability in this world.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.76,0:06:06.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kill or be killed!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.30,0:06:07.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your contact info...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.30,0:06:09.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ask for it or be asked for it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.05,0:06:12.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}It would be no overstatement to say therein\Nlies the person's superiority or inferiority!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.06,0:06:20.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Good grief. How much trouble does he think\NI went to just to make sure he got a phone?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.47,0:06:16.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Cheap cell phone!\NIt's got a cheap SIM card!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.77,0:06:21.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}SHINOMIYA\NHOUSE COOK
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.77,0:06:21.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an5}KAGUYA'S ATTENDANT
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.02,0:06:18.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}- Trendy! Trendy!\N- I'll send it over to you by Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.77,0:06:21.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an5}SHINOMIYA HOUSE GARDENER
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.52,0:06:25.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can finally contact the president\Noutside of school.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.86,0:06:29.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can say that my plan was a success,\Nby and large.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.03,0:06:34.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}I see. She wants to make me,\Nthe man, ask her!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.37,0:06:36.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}If that's how she wants to play it...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.75,0:06:41.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,President, this profile photo...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.63,0:06:44.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's a photo of me\Nfrom when I was a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.42,0:06:48.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's cute! You even scowled as a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.51,0:06:51.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}A photo of the president\Nfrom his childhood?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.38,0:06:51.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}You know how to hurt a guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.76,0:06:53.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}But that photo is a little embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.01,0:06:55.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I-I'm not especially interested.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.89,0:06:56.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}I think I'll change it to a different one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.02,0:06:58.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll change it in three minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.77,0:06:59.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}What?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.98,0:07:05.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}If the president changes his profile picture,\NI'll never be able to see that photo!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.40,0:07:07.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}But asking him for his contact info{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.49,0:07:11.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}expresses nothing other than\N"I want to talk to you anytime"!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.78,0:07:16.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}It means "I want to send\Ncasual messages before bedtime"...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.16,0:07:18.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}or "I want to talk to you on the phone...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.54,0:07:20.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}in the wee hours\Nthe night before a test and chat"!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.25,0:07:24.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}It'd be like that's what I was thinking!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.00,0:07:30.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}A lady must not do anything as improper\Nas asking a male for his contact information!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.47,0:07:33.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Since it's come to this,\NI'll have to use my last resort!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.72,0:07:39.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kaguya?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.44,0:07:45.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The president is so cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.82,0:07:46.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}DRIP
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.28,0:07:51.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,H-How could you be so mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.45,0:07:56.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her skill of deception has been activated!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.66,0:07:55.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}A MAIDEN’S TEARS
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.16,0:07:58.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}ACTIVATED
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.12,0:07:58.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're terrible, President!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.49,0:07:59.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.54,0:08:01.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her words don't especially mean anything.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.83,0:08:05.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}But being told he's mean makes him\Nfeel like he's done something mean.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.00,0:08:08.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}BARNUM EFFECT
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.96,0:08:08.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}In psychology,\Nit's called the "Barnum Effect."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.00,0:08:11.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! I didn't mean to leave you out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.76,0:08:13.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Here, I'll show you too, Shinomiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.72,0:08:16.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Wait. You...\N- Too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.55,0:08:18.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}She memorized it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.01,0:08:20.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Though it was a fleeting glimpse,\NShirogane's profile photo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.60,0:08:22.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}has been preserved\Nin Kaguya's hippocampus!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.06,0:08:26.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shirogane lost the sole ace up his sleeve!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.94,0:08:29.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kaguya made a comeback\Nto win overwhelmingly!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.61,0:08:36.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now, I have no reason\Nto ask the president for his ID.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.32,0:08:39.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Go ahead. Ask me for mine.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.91,0:08:42.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Can I... Can I come up with anything else?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.62,0:08:46.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shirogane racked his brain\Nto come from behind!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.63,0:08:48.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I guess I'll have to use that!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.38,0:08:51.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kaguya realized that she needed\Nto block that line of thinking!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.46,0:08:52.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's dead.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.34,0:08:53.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}The conclusion is at hand!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.26,0:08:56.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.18,0:09:02.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's cruel to talk about using Line when\NKaguya's old phone doesn't support that app!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.18,0:09:04.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.52,0:09:05.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- It can't use it?\N- It can't use it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.23,0:09:08.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're rich! Buy a different phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.02,0:09:10.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I've used this phone ever since kindergarten,\Nso I'm attached to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.98,0:09:12.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I can't switch it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.98,0:09:17.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an5}RESULTS OF TODAY'S MATCH
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.32,0:09:13.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Get rid of your weird hang-up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.32,0:09:17.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}This is a story of love and intellect\Ngoing around in circles.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.90,0:09:15.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,How is it weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.90,0:09:17.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}BOTH LOSE
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.53,0:09:17.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- I don't know if it's weird.\N- You're weird, President!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.95,0:09:21.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}THEY HAVE EXCHANGED ADDRESSES.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.75,0:09:25.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}It's cold today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.83,0:09:27.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}I wish summer would get here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.37,0:09:30.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}CHIKA WANTS\NTO GO SOMEWHERE
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.88,0:09:31.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Talk about impatient.\NIt'll be spring for a long time yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.21,0:09:34.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oh no! Time flies by way too fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.55,0:09:38.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}If you're careless, you'll graduate\Nwith nothing happening at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.26,0:09:39.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an5}80 DAMAGE TO THE HEARTS\NOF SHINOMIYA AND SHIROGANE
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.80,0:09:44.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Over the summer,\Nlet's go on a student council trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.60,0:09:46.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.31,0:09:48.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Let's go somewhere\Nlike an informal social gathering.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.81,0:09:50.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.06,0:09:51.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}A trip, huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.65,0:09:53.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then the mountains would be good.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.65,0:09:56.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fresh air.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.91,0:09:59.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Reverberating echoes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.62,0:10:03.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}SUMMIT
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.96,0:10:08.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}We'll rent a cottage and have a barbecue.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.79,0:10:12.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}At night, the starry sky will put a spell on us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.17,0:10:18.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Look. There's Deneb, Altair and Vega,\Nthe Summer Triangle.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.88,0:10:22.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Altair and Vega represent\Nthe story of Hikoboshi and Orihime.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.89,0:10:25.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're just like us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.68,0:10:27.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Close together...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.27,0:10:29.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}but so far apart.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.40,0:10:40.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}VEGA
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.40,0:10:41.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an5}DENEB
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.40,0:10:41.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an5}ALTAIR
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.86,0:10:44.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}No! President, I want to be Bb\Nto your Alpha Centauri B!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.54,0:10:47.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Please let me revolve\Naround you, President!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.67,0:10:50.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Oh, boy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.21,0:10:53.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}You're a pampered first-magnitude star.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.25,0:10:55.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an5}BOOM
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.04,0:10:55.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.46,0:10:57.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}It has to be the mountains!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.97,0:10:59.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes. If we're going, then—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.80,0:11:01.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It has to be the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.76,0:11:02.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Wha—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.39,0:11:04.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}The sea versus the mountains!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.97,0:11:08.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}The polar opposites that people\Nhave been fighting over since ancient times.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.27,0:11:11.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}The curtain rises\Non human nature's battle of thoughts.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.90,0:11:15.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}The sea. The sea is the origin of life.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.61,0:11:19.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}As the sun sets there, I'm sure humans\Nreturn to being creatures of instinct.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.49,0:11:26.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}My swimsuit will bewitch the president\Nthe second he sees it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.83,0:11:32.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}The sea will cast its spell\Non the president,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.25,0:11:34.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}and he'll confess his love to me\Nwhile the sun sets.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.71,0:11:38.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Perfect.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.26,0:11:42.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The roar of the sea\Nis the best lullaby in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.43,0:11:45.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And the salty sea breeze\Nwill blow away the summer heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.14,0:11:45.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}The sea?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.60,0:11:47.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}The sea is the last place I'll go!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.56,0:11:50.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't swim!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.64,0:11:52.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}NOTE: SINKS LIKE A HAMMER
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.52,0:11:55.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I went into the water\Nwith a swimming ring...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.90,0:11:58.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I didn't know you were\Na hopeless swimmer, President.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.65,0:12:01.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}How cute.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.32,0:12:03.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}No way! It has to be the mountains!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.45,0:12:04.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}I refuse to go to the sea!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.37,0:12:07.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The beach would be too crowded.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.20,0:12:08.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I hate bumping elbows with strangers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.79,0:12:12.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Let's use a private beach\Nowned by my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.75,0:12:15.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It has warm showers, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.04,0:12:17.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sunburn is a young lady's archenemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.13,0:12:19.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll bring along the highest grade sunscreen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.84,0:12:23.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And to seal the deal, I'll hire\Na first-class aesthetician for skin aftercare.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.88,0:12:28.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- There might be sharks.\N- I'll hire a first-class hunter from Florida.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.22,0:12:29.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Then we can have shark fin soup.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.85,0:12:29.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}COMFY
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.77,0:12:32.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn you, rich girl!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.85,0:12:35.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Weak sauce, President.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.56,0:12:42.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}THINGS THE PRESIDENT IS LIKELY TO SAY,\NVOL. 42, TRIP EDITION
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.86,0:12:40.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've already turned out a series of manuals\Nto prepare for when you oppose me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.19,0:12:42.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}However you attack me,\NI can render it harmless.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.70,0:12:45.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}We can only go to the sea\Nin the summer, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.20,0:12:48.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,With mountains,\Nyou can't depend on weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.03,0:12:49.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It rains a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.62,0:12:51.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Besides, it's got a lot of bugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.71,0:12:53.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bugs!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.87,0:12:59.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Moths, mosquitoes, horseflies, centipedes,\Nladybugs, earthworms, drone beetles...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.58,0:12:57.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bugs are the only thing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.42,0:13:01.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bugs are the only thing I can't stand!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.42,0:13:02.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}NOTE: HATES BUGS
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.01,0:13:05.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}What should I do?\NIf I go to the sea, I can't swim.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.55,0:13:07.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}If I go to the mountains,\Nthere are insects!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.27,0:13:14.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Guess I'll buy a swimsuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.56,0:13:15.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.73,0:13:17.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.52,0:13:20.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}My swimsuit from last year\Ndoesn't fit me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.52,0:13:22.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}I have to buy a new one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.57,0:13:30.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}FLAT
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.75,0:13:37.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Normally, Shinomiya\Nhas confidence in her body line.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.12,0:13:40.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}But take that away,\Nand her offensive ability becomes fragile...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.50,0:13:41.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Pop.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.21,0:13:43.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}on the level of a peashooter.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.63,0:13:47.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}On the other hand, Chika Fujiwara's\Noffensive ability is tank-class.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.30,0:13:49.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}The difference\Nin military strength is hopeless.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.30,0:13:51.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is bad!\NNever mind about enchanting him!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.60,0:13:55.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.23,0:13:59.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Compared to that, Shinomiya is...\NHow can I put it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.44,0:14:02.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}She has a cute chest?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.27,0:14:05.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Cute?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.90,0:14:07.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Let's go to the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.11,0:14:11.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The beach is too crowded,\Nand there are sharks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.03,0:14:13.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Let's go to the mountains.\N- You didn't say that before!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.29,0:14:14.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No, the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.54,0:14:17.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It rains in the mountains, and there are\Nlots of bugs! Let's go to the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.46,0:14:18.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.29,0:14:19.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- The mountains.\N- The sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.83,0:14:20.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Mountains.\N- Sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.75,0:14:21.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Mountains.\N- Sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.59,0:14:22.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Mountains.\N- Sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.00,0:14:25.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Since it's come to this,\Nhave Chika Fujiwara decide!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.59,0:14:26.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.55,0:14:27.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes, let's do it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.18,0:14:30.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}The sea. Got it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.30,0:14:33.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}The mountains!\NYou wouldn't betray me, would you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.14,0:14:36.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.64,0:14:38.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If I have to choose one...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.10,0:14:41.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The mountains?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.02,0:14:42.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.65,0:14:44.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But I specifically want to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.86,0:14:48.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,to Mount Osore!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.70,0:14:50.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mount Osore?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.33,0:14:55.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Children's Limbo and Blood Pond.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.66,0:14:57.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,There are pinwheels\Nsymbolizing death and rebirth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.96,0:15:02.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And as long as we're there,\Nlet's have a medium channel a spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.88,0:15:04.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Who would be good?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.59,0:15:06.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Christ? Buddha?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.88,0:15:08.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, I guess we can think about it\Nwhen summer comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.17,0:15:08.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Prince Shotoku could be good, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.26,0:15:14.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Aristotle, Shakespeare, Cleopatra,\NEinstein, Hideyoshi Toyotomi, Gandhi,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.18,0:15:10.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.93,0:15:12.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Today's match...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.47,0:15:14.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ruined.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.14,0:15:18.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sen no Rikyu, Caesar, Marie Antoinette,\NOscar Francois de Jarjayes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.39,0:15:18.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,BECAUSE CHIKA FUJIWARA\NIS A LITTLE SCARY
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.73,0:15:22.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an5}CHIKA FUJIWARA
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.94,0:15:25.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Romantic advice?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.69,0:15:28.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes! Where romance is concerned,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.40,0:15:29.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I thought a veteran like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.24,0:15:33.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}could give me advice, President!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.61,0:15:35.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}MIYUKI WANTS TO HIDE\NHIS IGNORANCE
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.99,0:15:38.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.75,0:15:41.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll help you somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.29,0:15:42.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,President!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.17,0:15:45.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}A romantic veteran?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.59,0:15:47.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}How did people get that image of me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.88,0:15:51.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Miyuki Shirogane, 17 years old.\NDating experience...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.51,0:15:52.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}None.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.93,0:16:03.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}NOTE: VIRGIN
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.80,0:15:56.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}What? If this advice exposes me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.89,0:15:58.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}The president is a virgin.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.48,0:16:00.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}A virgin?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.39,0:16:02.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm so disillusioned!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.94,0:16:05.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sh-Shinomiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.02,0:16:07.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,How cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.82,0:16:09.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}No! I have to get through this!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.99,0:16:12.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If it's about love, leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.28,0:16:16.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I've never been rejected before!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.53,0:16:18.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's why you're the president.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.08,0:16:20.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's never confessed his love,\Nso that's not actually a lie.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.37,0:16:23.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}The president is giving advice about love?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.46,0:16:26.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}This could be my chance\Nto hear his views on love!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.17,0:16:29.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So, what's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.17,0:16:36.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}KASHIWAGI
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.84,0:16:33.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I have a classmate, Kashiwagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.13,0:16:36.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I want to confess my love to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.56,0:16:38.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.72,0:16:41.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But when I imagine her rejecting me,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.43,0:16:44.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I think maybe I should\Nbecome friends with her first.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.11,0:16:48.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Incidentally,\Nhave you talked to her before?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.19,0:16:51.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,She gave me chocolate\Non Valentine's Day!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.90,0:16:53.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What kind of chocolate?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.53,0:16:55.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Choco Balls. Three pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.45,0:16:59.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Is that obligatory gift chocolate?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.03,0:17:01.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Obligatory gift chocolate at best!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.45,0:17:05.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yeah, I would say...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.33,0:17:07.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,she's definitely in love with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.92,0:17:08.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.04,0:17:10.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}He got Choco Balls!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.59,0:17:11.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.51,0:17:14.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Women are creatures\Nwho aren't upfront about their feelings!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.05,0:17:16.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Think of it as behaving\Nthe exact opposite of how they feel!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.93,0:17:19.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The Choco Balls seem\Nlike a throwaway, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.56,0:17:22.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an5}GASP
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.85,0:17:21.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It means she likes me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.06,0:17:22.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}What about opposites?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.39,0:17:25.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}All right! That sounded\Nlike half-decent advice!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.64,0:17:28.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But I don't think\Nshe does feel that way about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.81,0:17:30.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Just the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.19,0:17:34.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey, do you have a girlfriend?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.99,0:17:37.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, but...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.20,0:17:39.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I knew it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.53,0:17:41.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}He said he doesn't have a girlfriend!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.33,0:17:45.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}BOOM
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.83,0:17:43.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}He doesn't look like he has one!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.62,0:17:44.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's hilarious!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.17,0:17:52.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So, I think she was just making fun of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.01,0:17:55.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's unfortunate,\Nbut she was making fun of him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.38,0:17:58.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}The issue is whether she even sees him\Nas a member of the opposite sex.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.84,0:18:02.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're in your popular phase right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.10,0:18:06.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Why are you so suspicious of women?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.73,0:18:09.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Woman are humans, just like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.94,0:18:10.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}That's not what you were saying before!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.40,0:18:11.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll make that situation\Neasier to understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.48,0:18:16.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey, do you have a girlfriend?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.07,0:18:18.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If you don't, I wanna go out with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.03,0:18:21.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, but...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.62,0:18:22.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I knew it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.62,0:18:25.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}You and I are connected\Nby the string of fate!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.37,0:18:26.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}He said he doesn't have a girlfriend!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.83,0:18:30.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}BOOM
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.16,0:18:29.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}He doesn't look like he has one!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.71,0:18:30.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}THUMP-THUMP
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.12,0:18:31.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}After all, he's too high-class!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.71,0:18:34.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}BOOM
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.00,0:18:32.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's hilarious!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.21,0:18:34.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}THUMP-THUMP
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.46,0:18:34.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm thrilled that he's available!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.21,0:18:37.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}BOOM
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.09,0:18:37.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}THUMP-THUMP
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.34,0:18:37.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm the one who's most worthy of him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.59,0:18:39.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Isn't that thinking too positively?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.59,0:18:42.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.93,0:18:44.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Exactly!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.39,0:18:47.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I have to choose only one of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.81,0:18:49.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're an idiot, too?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.81,0:18:54.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Won't that cause a rift\Nin their friendship with each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.44,0:18:57.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Worst case, it could lead to bullying.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.70,0:19:00.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's what female friendship is like.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.20,0:19:02.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is this arrogant conversation?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.74,0:19:05.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But it'll be okay.\NBecause she'll have you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.41,0:19:08.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,All you have to do is protect her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.87,0:19:12.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I can... protect her?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.96,0:19:14.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- President!\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.55,0:19:15.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.92,0:19:18.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}This'll be my first time\Nconfessing my love to someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.34,0:19:20.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}How should I go about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.38,0:19:21.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}I have a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.01,0:19:26.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Imagine the girl in question is right here.\N- Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.68,0:19:28.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You do...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.10,0:19:30.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.15,0:19:35.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Go out with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.15,0:19:42.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,When you suddenly corner a girl\Nagainst the wall like that, she'll be nervous,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.74,0:19:44.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,but the moment\Nyou whisper of love in her ear,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.87,0:19:48.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,anxiety will turn into a throbbing heart.\NYour chance of success will go up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.08,0:19:50.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}He startled me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.58,0:19:54.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I call this technique "wall-down."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.75,0:19:55.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I came up with it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.88,0:19:58.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's "wall-slamming”!\NIt's been around for years!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.13,0:20:01.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}SHIVER SHIVER
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.01,0:20:00.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.05,0:20:01.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}You're that stupid?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.01,0:20:05.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thank you!\NYou've given me courage, President!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.76,0:20:08.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I knew the person who conquered\NShinomiya could help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.98,0:20:13.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No, Shinomiya and I aren't dating.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.65,0:20:16.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Th-That's right!\NNo one's ever conquered me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.77,0:20:18.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.28,0:20:21.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It seems like you two are a couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.03,0:20:22.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No, just the opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.24,0:20:26.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Recently, I wonder if she hates me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.20,0:20:29.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}I don't even think she's interested in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.16,0:20:32.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't especially hate you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.50,0:20:34.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did I do something to give you that idea?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.29,0:20:35.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}She has no self-awareness.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.54,0:20:39.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}President!\NWhat's important is how you feel!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.38,0:20:46.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,How do I feel about Shinomiya?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.60,0:20:53.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Well, to be honest, her wealth\Nand natural talents annoy me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.44,0:20:58.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}She's ditsier than you'd think,\Nscary in private, and her chest...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.11,0:21:02.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}But maybe those are all good points!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.03,0:21:05.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,She's actually cute! A beauty!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.03,0:21:09.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Refined, elegant and clever, too!\NReally, she's too perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.95,0:21:14.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah, Shinomiya is the ideal woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.59,0:21:20.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}That was close! She's right there!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.00,0:21:21.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thank God I noticed!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.09,0:21:25.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Anyway, nothing will happen\Nunless you tell her how you feel!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.34,0:21:28.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}And nothing good can come\Nof carrying out some weird scheme!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.39,0:21:32.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh? Why do these words resonate with me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.48,0:21:36.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I-I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.77,0:21:40.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.24,0:21:48.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kaguya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.70,0:21:51.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Has something good happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.49,0:21:53.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.96,0:21:55.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Afterwards...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.04,0:22:01.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}he confessed his feelings to Kashiwagi,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.71,0:22:04.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}and somehow\Nthey're apparently a couple now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.55,0:22:11.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,President, I poured you some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.89,0:22:14.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.73,0:22:17.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thankfully, she seems to be\Nin a good mood.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.19,0:22:20.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Today's match...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.19,0:22:20.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Is that your one smile\Nof the day?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.19,0:22:21.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kaguya wasn't particularly at fault...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.77,0:22:23.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}No, I'm like this\Nall the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.44,0:22:24.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}when Shirogane put her in a foul mood,\Nthen a good mood,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.36,0:22:24.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.32,0:22:27.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}but he largely wasted his efforts,\Nresulting in a loss for himself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.95,0:22:29.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an4}THE NEXT PERSON SEEKING ADVICE
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.41,0:22:29.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Shock!
